    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ct_88",
      "x": 5280,
      "y": 315,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "How it works:\n1. Upload a seed image or describe concept\n2. Claude Code generates ad copy + layout\n3. Airtable stores & tracks all variants\n4. Gemini/fal.ai generates final images",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "cb_87",
      "originalText": "How it works:\n1. Upload a seed image or describe concept\n2. Claude Code generates ad copy + layout\n3. Airtable stores & tracks all variants\n4. Gemini/fal.ai generates final images",
